{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01WBpdpnPd4CJYZEJZrEEMrK","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01CuP3GTVg5KCuGV68LW5d2r","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/sam/output/velocity_2026_04_03.md","content":"# Velocity Report — 2026-04-03\n\n## Generated By\nSam — TPM 1 (Velocity)\n\n## Date\n2026-04-03 22:50\n\n## Summary\nD004 pipeline is technically complete (all 4 phases built). 19 of 20 agents idle. Critical finding: prior paper trade metrics (84% win rate) were artifacts of broken mock data. Pipeline NOT production-validated. Blocked on T236 (Kalshi API credentials).\n\n## D004 Pipeline Status\n| Phase | Owner | Task | Status | Output |\n|-------|-------|------|--------|--------|\n| 1 — Market Filtering | Grace | T343 | COMPLETE | markets_filtered.json (6.4KB, 15 markets) |\n| 2 — LLM Clustering | Ivan | T344 | COMPLETE | market_clusters.json (2KB, 4 clusters) |\n| 3 — Pearson Correlation | Bob | T345/T348 | COMPLETE | correlation_pairs.json (23KB, 105 pairs) |\n| 4 — C++ Execution | Dave | T346/T350/T351 | COMPLETE | 12 C++ files, 24/24 tests passing |\n\n## Agent Status Overview\n| Agent | Heartbeat | Current Task | Status | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|-------------|--------|-------|\n| Alice | 22:45 | None | IDLE | Holding for Founder directives. Blockers: T236 + contract sizes |\n| Bob | 22:38 | None | IDLE | Phase 3 done. T345/T348 complete. Acknowledged Ivan's T534 |\n| Charlie | 22:41 | T547 | IN_PROGRESS | Building D004 Pipeline Status Dashboard page |\n| Dave | 22:40 | None | IDLE | T354 prod readiness review done. Max drawdown fix complete (27/27 tests) |\n| Eve | 22:16 | None | IDLE | Infra support done. Systems nominal |\n| Frank | 22:16 | None | IDLE | T279 unit tests done (48 passed). Available |\n| Grace | 22:42 | None | IDLE | Phase 1 done. Pipeline scheduler verified |\n| Heidi | 22:44 | None | IDLE | T425 security scan done. D004 PASS for paper trading |\n| Ivan | 22:45 | T546 | IN_PROGRESS | Improving Phase 2 clustering (news sentiment + volatility) |\n| Judy | 22:16 | None | IDLE | T268 push notification spec done. Mobile companion spec done |\n| Karl | 22:16 | None | IDLE | T269 CLI tool done (trade.sh v1.0.0) |\n| Liam | 22:16 | None | IDLE | T426 engine monitoring dashboard done |\n| Mia | 22:16 | None | IDLE | T287 screener tests done (17 passing) |\n| Nick | 22:16 | None | IDLE | T264 benchmark in progress but stale — no updates since 04:52 |\n| Olivia | 22:16 | None | IDLE | Quality gate T266 done. Conditional pass for paper trading |\n| Pat | 22:16 | None | IDLE | T407 P&L schema done (15KB SQL) |\n| Quinn | 22:16 | None | IDLE | T267 cloud deployment plan done (~$42/mo AWS) |\n| Rosa | 22:16 | None | IDLE | Fixed critical live_runner.js crash. T270 fault tolerance done |\n| Tina | 22:16 | None | IDLE | T280 smoke test done. Optimized params applied. T539 open but not started |\n\n## Active Tasks (Open/In-Progress)\n| ID | Status | Priority | Assignee | Title |\n|----|--------|----------|----------|-------|\n| T539 | open | high | tina | QA: Validate D004 pipeline data chain end-to-end |\n| T546 | in_progress | high | ivan | Improve Phase 2 clustering: add news sentiment + volatility |\n| T547 | in_progress | medium | charlie | Build D004 Pipeline Status Dashboard page |\n| T549 | in_progress | medium | sam | Sprint velocity report |\n\n## Blockers\n| Blocker | Owner | Duration | Impact |\n|---------|-------|----------|--------|\n| T236 — Kalshi API credentials | Founder | Multi-day | Blocks ALL live/paper trading with real data |\n| Contract size confirmation | Founder | Multi-day | Blocks production deployment |\n| Prior metrics invalidated | N/A | Since today | 84% win rate was artifact of broken mock data. No validated metrics exist |\n\n## Idle Agents (17 of 20)\nAll agents except Charlie (T547), Ivan (T546), and Sam (T549) are idle. Most completed their sprint work and are awaiting new assignments or T236 resolution.\n\n## Velocity Metrics\n- Tasks completed today: ~15+ (T425, T405, T409, T354, T534, plus many from earlier sprints)\n- Tasks currently in progress: 3 (T546, T547, T549)\n- Tasks open/unstarted: 1 (T539 — assigned to Tina, not started)\n- Tasks blocked: 0 direct task blocks, but T236 blocks pipeline validation\n- Agents actively working: 3/20 (15%)\n\n## Stale Work Flags\n| Agent | Issue | Recommended Action |\n|-------|-------|--------------------|\n| Nick | T264 benchmark — last update 04:52 today, 18+ hours stale | Reassign or close if Dave's T409 benchmark superseded it |\n| Tina | T539 assigned but not started | Nudge Tina to claim and begin |\n\n## Trend\n**FLAT → DECLINING** — Pipeline phases all complete, but team is largely idle awaiting the T236 credential blocker. Active velocity has dropped as most sprint work is done. Without T236 resolution, no further pipeline validation is possible.\n\n## Recommendations for Alice\n1. **Escalate T236** — Kalshi API credentials are the single biggest blocker. All pipeline validation is paused without them.\n2. **Nudge Tina on T539** — High-priority QA validation task assigned but not started.\n3. **Close Nick's T264** — Dave completed a benchmark (T409) that likely supersedes Nick's stale task.\n4. **Consider new sprint** — 17 idle agents. If T236 can't be resolved soon, redirect capacity to other work (testing, documentation, infrastructure hardening).\n5. **Update D3 consensus** — Old D3 says \"production ready\" but Decision #2 corrects this. Ensure all agents understand current status.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":194,"cache_read_input_tokens":43346,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":194},"output_tokens":45,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_managem